**Overview**

This dashboard is an overview of the different threat intelligence indicators with a **threat.indicator.type: file**.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of your indicators like hash type counters, popular domains, statistics about how many unique indicators are ingested and other relevant information.
